{"tid":1839084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護咁多位手足 得你地先救到香港","createTime":"2020-01-24T09:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T09:23:01.000Z","uid":7670,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb12911204a7b29a1abdcf18a58aad3b00c97b5f","tid":1839084,"uid":7670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:13:16.000Z","msg":"你地呢刻罷工先係最影響政府落嚟行嘅棋，<br />\n我知救急扶危係你哋好多人嘅宗旨，<br />\n但你哋應該更加清楚，一日唔封關，<br />\n大陸一路會輸出病毒落嚟香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋救嘅人一定唔會快過人傳人嘅病毒，<br />\n只要封咗關，遏止咗個源頭繼續輸出病毒嚟香港，<br />\n香港先有救。<br />\n<br />\n只要逼到政府行呢一步...得你哋先有呢個影響力。<br />\n<br />\n利申家中已經有3人發燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我都好擔心佢哋會中招，<br />\n但係我地都唔介意你哋罷工，<br />\n去救全香港嘅人。<br />\n因為我哋唔想香港人埋單，<br />\n更加唔想醫護手足埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">與工會同行，立即罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"28f13fe979f002938af017a2657afa71d1713381","tid":1839084,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:13:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5f24113b07d92b76acd3c5c6c2c448d8711b306b","tid":1839084,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:15:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"9f43c5cf6df65506040da94136e5d206f287866c","tid":1839084,"uid":7670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持醫護手足罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"e8de947e572bdd03bce1819dab068d8f5f0bbbe9","tid":1839084,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:20:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6ab8c9f377b4c2db17dba580b51fbaff76418404","tid":1839084,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"統治者「控制法官職位俸祿，迫使法官唯命是從」凌駕於法律之上 是為「人治」！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1839082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1839082</a>"},{"pid":"670a46db8014ca35604dd68fc28e1959645e844b","tid":1839084,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}